Package tempest_foundation.ClassElements

Class Function

java.lang.Object
tempest_foundation.SubmissionElements.MarkSnippet
tempest_foundation.ClassElements.Function
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClassE
public class Function extends MarkSnippet
The Function class represents a function or method in a program. It extends MarkSnippet and contains information about the function's name, return type, visibility, parameters, variables, and content. The class provides methods for analyzing and processing function details.
